# Class: obo:OBI_0000260 (plan)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:OBI_0000260 "A plan is a realizable entity that is the inheres in a bearer who is committed to realizing it as a completely executed planned process."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:OBI_0000260 "plan"@en)
